### POST /api/v1/trips/{id}/complete
### Descripción: Completar viaje. Requiere Driver o Admin. Opcional: distanceKm, durationMinutes.
### Headers requeridos: Authorization: Bearer <token>
### Códigos: 200 OK (TripDto) | 403 | 404 | 422

# @name completeTrip
POST {{BASE_URL}}/api/v1/trips/{{TRIP_ID}}/complete
Authorization: Bearer {{ACCESS_TOKEN}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "distanceKm": 5.2,
  "durationMinutes": 18
}

### Response esperado (200): TripDto
### Response error (422): INVALID_TRANSITION, etc.
